- [ ] Download from 
[] https://sourceforge.net/projects/iverilog/

% tar -zxvf verilog-version.tar.gz

% cd verilog-version

- [ ] Fellow instructuion from
[] https://iverilog.fandom.com/wiki/Installation_Guide

% ./configure  

- [ ] View the error log by(after run ./configure)
+ gvim config.log

- [ ] Fix the error by installing by 
% sudo yum install flex

% sudo yum install bison

% sudo yum install g++

% sudo yum install gcc-c++

- [ ] Try again
% ./configure  

% make  

% (su to root)  # make install

